Lice coming out of the hair in a dream. Seeing lice in a dream may symbolize collecting money. Engaging in projects to increase profit, or an indication of removing anxiety from the dreamer’s heart regarding the danger that may pass at any moment. Seeing lice on the ground symbolizes a weak enemy surrounding him, or an indication of the dreamer’s personality that needs to be corrected and reformed, and God knows best. The scholar Ibn Sirin has another opinion regarding the interpretation of seeing lice in general in a dream. Whoever dreams that lice are walking on the ground, this symbolizes the dreamer’s companionship with the weak who suffer from shame but will not be harmed by their company. Lice in the dream is evidence of enemies who seek to harm the dreamer, causing him pain. Lice in the hair is evidence of the dreamer’s close enemy who may be one of his relatives. Or his friends. As for the interpretation of lice emerging from the hair, it indicates relief from the distress that the dreamer is suffering from, recovering from illness, obtaining a reward, enjoying comfort, changing circumstances from bad to better, and multiple gains. The dream also symbolizes getting rid of the problems that stood in the dreamer’s way in achieving his dreams. Also, seeing lice coming out of the hair in the dream indicates exposure to worries from oneself, freedom from problems and diseases, and the ability to reveal everything that is going on around him, and God knows best. Explanation of cleaning hair From lice: Whoever dreams that he is cleaning his hair from lice, this is a sign of expelling negative energy from the body and liberation from any unrestrained desire within it. Recover and enjoy good health.
